dct_description_sm: "Modified master plan showing suggested amendments to Highway Network, Central Area Location and Programme." [Map is part of: "Northumberland County Development Plan. Written analysis", pub. 1963.] The Map Library does not have this report. Map no.: D/C.N.T./3.1. "This plan is based upon the Ordnance Survey Map with the sanction of the Controller of H.M. Stationary Office.".
